---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="freeofmoney.pro"
  description="freeofmoney.pro：书籍与个人项目主页。"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="kicker">Book Shelf · Notes · Projects</p>
    <h1>Free Of Money</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      这是我的公开工作台。先把最近在读的一本书放上来，后续继续补充读书笔记和项目进展。
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="#book">在线阅读</a>
      <a class="button" href="/books/CZ_币安人生.pdf" download>下载 PDF</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="book" class="panel">
    <h2>本周在读</h2>
    <div class="book-meta">
      <p><strong>书名：</strong>幣安人生：幸運、韌性與保護用戶的回憶錄</p>
      <p><strong>作者：</strong>Zhao, Changpeng</p>
      <p><strong>页数：</strong>240 页</p>
      <p><strong>格式：</strong>PDF</p>
    </div>
    <div class="book-actions">
      <a class="button primary" href="/books/CZ_币安人生.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">新窗口预览</a>
      <a class="button" href="/books/CZ_币安人生.pdf" download>下载到本地</a>
    </div>
    <div class="pdf-frame-wrap">
      <iframe
        title="幣安人生 PDF 预览"
        src="/books/CZ_币安人生.pdf#view=FitH"
        class="pdf-frame"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="now" class="panel">
    <h2>Now</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>把常读书单和笔记同步到主页。</li>
      <li>维护自动化流程与知识库。</li>
      <li>持续迭代个人工具和小型产品。</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="projects" class="panel">
    <h2>Projects (Next)</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Knowledge OS</h3>
        <p>整理通讯录知识库与检索流程，降低信息查找成本。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>OpenClaw Ops</h3>
        <p>持续修复执行链路和记忆机制，提升稳定性与可验证性。</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Automation Stack</h3>
        <p>把日常检查和任务触发做成标准化流水线。</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
